### Creer une tache
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Implémenter la page de login",
  "description": "Créer le formulaire avec validation",
  "status": "todo",
  "priority": "high",
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}",
  "assigneeId": "{{assigneeId}}"
}

### Creer une tache sans assignee
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Faire un backup BDD",
  "status": "todo",
  "priority": "medium",
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}"
}

### Lister les taches
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Recuperer une tache par ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Modifier une tache - passer en IN_PROGRESS
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in_progress"
}

### Modifier une tache - augmenter priorite
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "priority": "medium"
}

### Marquer comme DONE
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "done"
}

### Reassigner une tache
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assigneeId": "{{assigneeId}}"
}

### Supprimer une tache
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test erreur: projectId invalide -> 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test",
  "projectId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### Test erreur: assignee invalide -> 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test",
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}",
  "assigneeId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}
